{"tid":1721872,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"升級左四日，我想問區選取消未啊？有冇人答到我啊。","createTime":"2019-11-14T19:01:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-14T19:09:22.000Z","uid":167548,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"9293c2d7f10e184dfe067ad3ffe74716691039af","tid":1721872,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T19:01:21.000Z","msg":"香港人醒下啦！佢最驚你升級啊！佢會利用區選製造民意假象！等沉默嘅大多數爆曬出嚟指責國際社會干涉香港內政<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 再重申區選是BONUS<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n曾經見過有文寫話爆出強姦案是鬼逼出嚟, 目的意圖停止區選<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 呢班分析師靠佢地引領運動死得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申香港獨立 <br />\n請幫手去推隔離個獨立Post<br />\n逼走班左膠時機撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb459776c65274b63e7484527225a4efd759465b","tid":1721872,"uid":194399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T19:06:34.000Z","msg":"______________________________________<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><ins>「請廣傳」香港黑警濫權資料庫 (中英日語） </ins></span></strong><br />\n依個網手足籌劃左好一段時間, 包含大量核彈, 請各位出分力廣傳<br />\n<a href=\"http://tl.hkrev.info/police-timeline/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftl.hkrev.info%2Fpolice-timeline%2F&d=zfTWtzkQ24d%2FEmJzkWMc62jFlCc76q8eB7f9T8a%2Fn1E%3D&h=3e8bc7c4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">tl.hkrev.info/police-timeline/</a>"},{"pid":"48c771da54ce93b1896c59254295e43281d1ce38","tid":1721872,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T19:08:37.000Z","msg":"真是好好笑 香港人用五大訴求去包裝香港獨立, 就好似藍絲咁自己呃埋自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你地唔好期望黃絲就聰明啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 淺黃大多是感情用事<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9393e49f76bb8af9af9e3dcf7b1dbc02342f975","tid":1721872,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sc